      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've ever tried sending cold emails manually, you know the drill: juggling multiple inboxes, worrying about deliverability, writing the same pitch seventeen different ways, and crossing your fingers that Gmail doesn't tank your sender reputation by Thursday.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://refer.instantly.ai/ndtfrl3h0x5l"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instantly",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " eliminates all of that friction. It's a cold email platform built for one specific job — sending outreach at massive scale without burning your domains or drowning in busywork. And it does that job absurdly well.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent weeks testing the platform, digging through features, and mapping out the exact workflows that make Instantly shine. This guide covers the best tips, newest features, and most effective ways to squeeze every drop of value out of it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
