        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Exactly Is Instantly and How Does It Work?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-instantly"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instantly",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is a cold email outreach platform that lets you connect unlimited email accounts, automatically warm up new domains, and send personalized sequences powered by AI.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's the basic flow:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Connect your email accounts.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You can add as many as you want — Gmail, Outlook, custom SMTP, whatever you use.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Warm up your domains.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Instantly sends and receives emails between a network of real inboxes, building your sender reputation before you launch campaigns.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Build your sequences.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Write your email copy (or let the AI help), set your sending schedules, and define follow-up rules.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Launch and monitor.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Track opens, replies, bounces, and warmup scores from a single dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The beauty is in the automation. You set it up once, and Instantly handles the rest — rotating between accounts, staggering sends to stay under provider limits, and pausing accounts that show warning signs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-instantly"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a deeper walkthrough, check our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Instantly tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New and Highlighted Features Worth Your Attention",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instantly ships updates fast. Here are the standout features that make the platform feel genuinely modern:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Sequence Writing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You don't have to stare at a blank email draft anymore. Instantly's AI generates subject lines, opening lines, and full follow-up sequences based on your product description and target audience. It's not generic template filler — the AI adapts tone, length, and hooks based on the context you provide. You can regenerate individual lines or entire emails until they sound exactly like you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unlimited Email Accounts",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the feature that changed the game for cold email. Most competitors cap you at 5, 10, or maybe 20 accounts. Instantly lets you connect as many as you want. Why does this matter? Because sending 50 emails per day from 20 accounts looks natural to inbox providers. Sending 1,000 emails from one account looks like spam. Instantly makes scaling safe by design.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automated Warmup Network",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every connected account enters Instantly's warmup pool. The system sends real emails between accounts, opens them, marks them as important, removes them from spam, and even replies — all automatically. Your warmup score climbs over days, and you can monitor it in real time. When an account hits a healthy score, you know it's ready for outreach.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lead Database and Finder",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instantly recently added a built-in lead finder with over 160 million contacts. You can filter by job title, industry, location, company size, and more — then push leads directly into your campaigns. No more exporting CSVs from three different tools.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CRM Integration",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform now includes a lightweight CRM that tracks leads through pipeline stages. For teams that want everything in one place, this eliminates the need to sync data between separate tools. You can see which leads replied, which need follow-up, and which converted — all without leaving Instantly.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A/Z Testing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instead of standard A/B testing, Instantly lets you test up to 26 variations of a single email. Different subject lines, different opening hooks, different CTAs — you get statistically significant results faster, which means you optimize your messaging in days instead of weeks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/instantly-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For the latest releases, bookmark our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instantly new features roundup",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Best Tips and Ways to Get Maximum Results with Instantly",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Knowing the features is one thing. Using them strategically is where the magic happens. Here are the practices that separate users who get 5% reply rates from those who get 20%+.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 1: Warm Up Every Domain for at Least 2-3 Weeks",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't rush this. Even though Instantly's warmup engine is fast, inbox providers like Google are increasingly suspicious of new domains that suddenly blast emails. Let the warmup score reach at least 85-90% before launching your first campaign. Your future self will thank you when your emails land in primary inboxes instead of promotions or spam.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 2: Rotate Between Multiple Sending Accounts",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set your campaigns to rotate across 5-10 accounts per campaign. Instantly handles this automatically, but you should configure the rotation limits based on each provider's thresholds. For Gmail, stay under 50 cold emails per account per day. For Outlook, you can push slightly higher. The platform lets you set these limits per account, so use that control.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 3: Use Spintax and Personalization Variables",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Generic emails get ignored. Instantly supports spintax (randomized word variations) and personalization tokens (first name, company, job title, custom fields). Combine both. A subject line like \"{Hi|Hey|Hello} {{first_name}} — quick question about {{company}}\" creates dozens of unique variations that avoid spam filters and catch attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 4: Write Short, Conversational Sequences",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The best-performing cold emails read like messages from a colleague, not marketing copy. Keep your first email under 80 words. Ask one clear question. In follow-ups, add new value each time — a relevant case study, a specific insight about their company, a different angle on the same problem. Instantly makes it easy to chain 4-6 follow-ups with smart delays between them.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 5: Leverage the AI for Subject Line Testing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Subject lines are 80% of the battle. Use Instantly's AI to generate 10-15 options, then A/Z test the top 5. Look for patterns in what works — sometimes questions outperform statements, sometimes numbers outperform words. The AI accelerates this discovery process dramatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 6: Segment Your Lead Lists Before Sending",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't dump 10,000 leads into a single campaign. Segment by industry, company size, or job title, and tailor your messaging to each segment. Instantly's lead finder makes this easy — filter, save, and assign each list to a dedicated campaign with matching copy. Relevance is the single biggest driver of reply rates.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-instantly"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want more strategies? Our guide on ",
            "marks": []
