            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instantly isn't trying to be everything to everyone. It's laser-focused on people and teams who send cold email as a core part of their revenue engine. Here's who benefits most:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sales Development Representatives (SDRs)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — If your daily job involves prospecting and booking meetings, Instantly is purpose-built for your workflow. The unlimited accounts, automated warmup, and AI sequences let you focus on conversations instead of logistics.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lead Generation Agencies",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Agencies managing outreach for multiple clients need separation between accounts and campaigns. Instantly handles this cleanly, letting you run dozens of client campaigns from one dashboard without cross-contamination.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Solo Founders and Bootstrapped Startups",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Early-stage founders who can't afford a full sales team can use Instantly to generate their first pipeline of meetings. The pricing is accessible, and the AI writing assistance means you don't need copywriting expertise.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Recruiters",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Outreach for hiring follows the same principles as sales outreach. Instantly works beautifully for recruiters reaching passive candidates at scale, with personalized sequences that reference specific roles and company culture.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "B2B Service Providers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Consultants, agencies, and freelancers selling high-ticket services use Instantly to fill their calendars with discovery calls. The ability to hyper-personalize at scale makes it possible to pitch enterprise clients without feeling robotic.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
